  "title": "Part-time admin",
  "description": "<p>This is a <u>permanent</u> part-time administrative role at Wee Swee Teow LLP in River Valley (Valley Point) . You will be responsible for providing essential administrative and client support to ensure the smooth operation of the office. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>S$13 per hour depending on experience and suitability.</p>\n<p>Preferred working days:  9am to 6pm (Mon and Tues), 11am to 4pm (Monday, Tues and Fri) </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What you'll be doing</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Answering and directing incoming phone calls and emails</li>\n  <li>Maintaining client records and databases.</li>\n  <li>Providing general administrative support, such as filing, photocopying, and data entry</li>\n  <li>Ad-hoc despatch of documents</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proficient in using Microsoft Office suite (Word, Excel, Outlook)</li>\n  <li>Effective communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>A proactive, reliable, and flexible approach to work</li>\n</ul>",
