    "uen": "T17LL0017L",
    "description": "<p>Wee Swee Teow LLP is one of Singapore's oldest law firms, having been etablished in 1912 under the name of Wee Swee Teow &amp; Co by its eponymous founder, who was one of the leading Chancery lawyers of his time. Beginning with a strong focus in trust, estate and real estate, the firm has over the years broadened its areas of specialisation. Today, we have an established reputation in arbitration and dispute resolution, corporate law, real estate and property, construction, equity and trust, wills and estate planning, &nbsp;and family law. We continue to grow our suite of services to reach beyond Singapore's shores as we serve the evolving needs of our clients around the world. We provide personalised and knowledgeable service to our clients even as we seek to be a responsible corporate citizen.</p>",
